system_info:

    name: ubuntu
    ssh_authorized_keys:
      - "ssh-rsa  iangeorge@MacBook-Air.local"

      - "ssh-rsa  wasimdanyal@Wasims-MacBook-Pro.local"

    groups: [adm, cdrom, dip, lxd, sudo]

runcmd:

  - cd ..
  - mkdir /data
  - mount -t efs -o tls,iam fs-0cae71b37cc064a4b:/ /data
  - /usr/local/bin/bootstrap.sh

packages:

  - binutils

write_files:
- encoding: b64
  content: 
  owner: root:root
  path: /usr/local/bin/bootstrap.sh
  permissions: '0700'
- encoding: b64
  content: 
  owner: root:root
  path: /etc/memgraph/memgraph.conf
  permissions: '0700'
- encoding: b64
  content: 
  owner: root:root
  path: /etc/systemd/system/memgraph-lab.service
  permissions: '0700'

runcmd:
  - git clone https://github.com/aws/efs-utils
  - cd efs-utils
  - ./build-deb.sh
  - apt -y install ./build/amazon-efs-utils*deb
  - cd ..
  - mkdir /data
  - mount -t efs -o tls,iam fs-0d76cb11bf44da0ee:/ /data

extra_params.description: Extra ssm parameters required. Values will not be managed by terraform after the parameter is created

extra_secrets.description: Extra secretsmanager secrets required. Values will not be managed by terraform after the secret is created

run_commands.constant_value:
python3.10 -m pip install networkx scipy
mkdir -p /data/memgraph_data /data/memgraph_logs /data/memgraph
wget https://download.memgraph.com/memgraph/v2.10.0/ubuntu-22.04/memgraph_2.10.0-1_amd64.deb
dpkg --force-confdef -i memgraph_2.10.0-1_amd64.deb
chown memgraph:memgraph /etc/memgraph/memgraph.conf
chown -R memgraph:memgraph /data/memgraph_data /data/memgraph_logs /data/memgraph
chmod 740 -R /data/memgraph_data /data/memgraph_logs /data/memgraph
echo "fs.file-max=100000" >> /etc/sysctl.conf
echo "vm.max_map_count=262144" >> /etc/sysctl.conf
sudo sysctl -p
echo "memgraph soft stack 8087482" >> /etc/security/limits.conf
echo "memgraph hard stack 8087482" >> /etc/security/limits.conf
systemctl stop memgraph
rm -rf /data/memgraph_data/settings/LOCK
systemctl start memgraph
docker rm memgraph
systemctl start memgraph-lab
systemctl enable memgraph-lab

extra_params.description: Extra ssm parameters required. Values will not be managed by terraform after the parameter is created

extra_secrets.description: Extra secretsmanager secrets required. Values will not be managed by terraform after the secret is created

run_commands.constant_value:
curl https://ollama.ai/install.sh | sh
mkdir -p /etc/systemd/system/ollama.service.d
mkdir -p /data/models
chgrp ollama /data/models
chmod g+w /data/models
echo '[Service]' >> /etc/systemd/system/ollama.service.d/environment.conf
echo 'Environment=OLLAMA_HOST=0.0.0.0:11434' >> /etc/systemd/system/ollama.service.d/environment.conf
echo 'Environment=OLLAMA_MODELS=/data/models' >> /etc/systemd/system/ollama.service.d/environment.conf
sleep 10
systemctl daemon-reload
systemctl restart ollama
ollama serve
ollama pull mistral
ollama pull llama2
ollama pull llama2:13b
